
                     HOW TO WRITE AMIGAGUIDE DOCUMENTS
                     =================================

                                INSTALLATION
                                ============

To install this project, simply copy the complete "How To Write Amigaguide"
drawer to wherever you like.

Make sure that it has these contents:-

  Amigaguide_How_To_Write (Dir)
    AGHTW_Boring_Stuff
    AGHTW_Index
    AGHTW_Part1
    AGHTW_Part2
    AGHTW_Part3
    AGHTW_Part4
    AGHTW_Part5
    aguidehowwrite.readme           *
    How_To_Write_Amigaguide
    How_To_Write_Amigaguide.info
    Installation                    *
    Installation.info               *

  Help (Sub Dir)
    ExtraNotes

  Miscellaneous (Sub Dir)
    adosbegin.readme
    AG_Settings
    amigalogo.pic
    arexxbegin.readme
    AssignAGHTW
    BasicDoc.guide
    Cuckoo.snd
    DemoScript
    Demo_Of_Settings.guide
    Demo_Of_Settings.rexx
    helpdoc.guide
    MV_Settings
    ShowNodeExample-1.rexx
    ShowNodeExample-2.rexx
    Testprogram.guide
    Testprogram_close.rexx
    Testprogram_open.rexx


* These files can be deleted if you want to.

Then just double click on the "How To Write Amigaguide" icon and you are up
and running!

